// Open the map
PressKey(77);
Delay(50);
ReleaseKey(77);
//WriteToLog(Starting!);

// Add time for Detector to finish
Delay(1500);

// Click search-icon
PushLeftButton(67,547);
Delay(50);
PullLeftButton(0,0);

// Navigate to Zak Waypoint
// Double-click on Zak Left+Right to remove "Teleport" marker.
Delay(500);
PushLeftButton(209,467);
Delay(100);
PullLeftButton(0,0);
Delay(500);
PushRightButton(201,459);
Delay(100);
PullRightButton(0,0);

Delay(500);

IF FindPixel(243,214,22,922,748,71,127);
// Goto location 2
Delay(250);
PlayScript();
ENDIF;
Delay(100);

IF FindPixel(243,214,22,760,788,72,161);
// Goto location 3
Delay(250);
PlayScript();
ENDIF;
Delay(100);

IF FindPixel(243,214,22,835,916,167,71);
// Goto location 4
Delay(250);
PlayScript();
ENDIF;
Delay(100);

IF FindPixel(243,214,22,843,799,51,101);
// Goto location 1
Delay(250);
PlayScript();
ENDIF;

// If the standard-navigation is still up - we click it.

PlayScript();
ENDIF;
